  "author_association": "MEMBER",
  "body": "Rook currently uses 3 different service accounts: rook-operator, rook-api, rook-ceph-osd.  We need to straighten out the following:\r\n* Should cluster components (OSDs, mons, etc.) each have their own service account, or just 1 service account that they all use?\r\n    * rook-operator needs to be cross namespace and it should only be used by the operator and agents.\r\n* rook-ceph-osd should be scoped to just its namespace (i.e., it should be using a `role` not a `clusterrole`)\r\n    * should rook-api be scoped to a single namespace this way as well? ",
